# Steam Backend

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Create .env file:
STEAM_API_KEY=your_key

3. Run migrations:
python manage.py migrate

4. Start server:
python manage.py runserver

## API

POST /api/register/
POST /api/login/
GET /api/search/?query=...
GET /api/h
